-----------------------------

I know. 

How you feel. 

And why... /really why/...

-------------------------
------------
---

&quot;We are too numb or too stupid to look up and see the things happening around us.&quot;

They made us like that... They did it to us.

&quot;In the middle of things it is hard to see the big picture.&quot;

...for most people, yes..

&quot;I feel so tired, so helpless.&quot;

That's what /it/ does to you. 

And they just love it... the fact that they've hurt you - hurt so many, dumbed 
us down, and utterly destroyed some of us, and put people in zombie like state.. 

They revel in destroying innocence......... 

------
------

&quot;I believe that people can make a difference. I believe that we could make a change, stop the fall, turn things into a better direction. I believe that we could make things better if we only tried.&quot;

Oh! We can! Oh, yes indeed, we /can/ do it.

&quot;If you only cared.&quot;

I for one, do. 

There are maaany, many tens of millions of people worldwide - who care. 
Many care, but still do nothing. However, millions are doing /something/. 

And countless thousands /are active/ in spreading the truth and waking people up! 

You are far from alone, Pao.
